steps-informal.p:
Specify one or more fallback font(s) in your customization
              CSS:body{
  font-family: Roboto, "Segoe UI", "Arial Unicode MS";
}




To determine the needed font, you can copy the text fragment from the DITA
                  source document and paste it into any text editor (e.g. MS Word). Make sure there
                  are no licensing restrictions on that particular font.
